{"tid":2307814,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃避雖可恥但有用SP】新垣結衣做人母湊bb　星野源變男人公敵？","createTime":"2020-12-01T11:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T21:11:28.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"adf9a1a469773e7ea85a56c612c9d49dff12045a","tid":2307814,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201201/410490877845180416896175.jpeg/VnWrOwGssn40QMjh7lGVUXez3KAU0g3PwkTwTsJE8E4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201201%2F410490877845180416896175.jpeg%2FVnWrOwGssn40QMjh7lGVUXez3KAU0g3PwkTwTsJE8E4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e0f63ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由新垣結衣與星野源主演的《逃避雖可恥但有用》新春SP（Special的縮寫）篇即將在明年1月播放，片長長達2小時25分鐘。劇集的預告昨日（30日）在YouTube上架，距離第一季已經相隔4年，不少劇迷垣言相當期待二人的演出。<br />\n<br />\n從預告中可看見新春SP篇內容講到二人的新婚生活，新垣結衣更會成為人母，片中二人對於迎接新生命開心之餘也顯得手足無措，當新手父母期間亦有不少搞笑位令觀眾等不及要追看，不過有一部份網友似乎接受不了結衣BB做人母，表示：「我接受唔到囉」、「星野源係男人公敵」、「我個結衣BB呀，嗚」"},{"pid":"e9497362e8184874449e22b7bde0e71a33651f00","tid":2307814,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"想同結衣結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d719130b534b23f2f2a6710f8290a706bc7e144","tid":2307814,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9497362e8184874449e22b7bde0e71a33651f00","tid":2307814,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"想同結衣結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:56:21.000Z","msg":"老了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57537d355a5127f6056724f54aeecdfe85ea87b","tid":2307814,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d719130b534b23